{
  "stem": "2118.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he went to work as a weaver, which consisted in a-- it was home work-- not at our home, but at-- it was somebody had let's say two, three weaving machines.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was done by hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he went there in order to learn as an apprentice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when the war broke out, he was already making about, oh, maybe 15, 20 zlotys a week, which was considered good money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Even a much older working man wasn't making more than that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the idea was that to set him up into this business, buy a few machines, work a little himself, and then gradually have people work for him, which was very common in the city of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was the youngest, and I finished school in 1938.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the-- the neighborhood we lived in, or the whole neighborhood, all of Balut, was a weaving neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The-- most people were weavers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was-- this was the-- the income people had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took home work from the big factories, and they done it at home at the-- at-- piece for it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, they paid that much for each meter, which is a yard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were doing those heavy clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How would I say this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What they used for-- you know, when-- when it was winter cold, the woman went out, and she did-- she didn't put on a coat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She took that-- it was like a-- A cape?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If wasn't even a cape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a square thing with a nice fringe, and she wrapped herself around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was real warm-- real good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was big.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not shawl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In summertime, it was shawl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did that-- they did that too in summertime.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
